| **Module 8 --- What the Attacker Left Behind**                        |
|                                                                       |
| A09 Logging & Monitoring Failures \| Three-Stage Lab Exercise         |
|                                                                       |
| *BBC Academy / JBI Training \| Uses: vulnerable_shop.py,              |
| vulnerable_shop_fixed.py, OWASP Juice Shop*                           |
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------+

  -----------------------------------------------------------------------
  **Juice Shop connection:** this exercise uses the ShopCo Flask app from
  Module 4 to demonstrate the A09 failure mode --- then maps what you
  observe directly to vulnerabilities you have already found in Juice
  Shop\'s own incomplete logging.

  -----------------------------------------------------------------------

